skill.name: The Darkin Blade
skill.desc: Aatrox cleaves the area in front of him, dealing damage to enemies inside it.

skill.name: Orb of Deception
skill.desc: Ahri fires an orb in a line that returns to her, damaging enemies it passes through.

skill.name: Five Point Strike
skill.desc: Akali throws shurikens in front of her, dealing damage. This spell can critically strike.

skill.name: Glacial Storm
skill.desc: Anivia channels a large hailstorm, damaging and slowing the attack speed of enemies inside of it.

skill.name: Enchanted Crystal Arrow
skill.desc: Ashe fires an arrow that stuns and damages the farthest enemy. The stun is longer the farther the enemy.

skill.name: Voice of Light
skill.desc: Aurelion Sol breathes a large blast of fire in a line, dealing damage to enemies.

skill.name: Rocket Grab
skill.desc: Blitzcrank pulls the furthest enemy to him and stuns them for 2.5s.

skill.name: Pyroclasm
skill.desc: Brand launches a bouncing fireball, damaging enemies hit.

skill.name: Unbreakable
skill.desc: Braum gains a barrier that blocks incoming damage.

skill.name: The Hextech Ultimatum
skill.desc: Camille singles out an enemy, dealing magic damage and rooting them. Camille's allies in range will prioritize attacking that enemy.

skill.name: Rupture
skill.desc: Cho'gath ruptures an area, stunning and damaging enemies inside of it.

skill.name: Decimate
skill.desc: Darius swings his axe, damaging nearby enemies and healing himself based off enemies hit.

skill.name: Spinning Axes
skill.desc: Draven gains Spinning Axes, dealing bonus on-hit damage. Stacks up to two times.

skill.name: Spider Form
skill.desc: Elise summons Spiderlings and transforms, gaining Lifesteal.

skill.name: Last Caress
skill.desc: Evelynn deals damage to the 3 closest enemies and teleports away. Damage is increased against low health enemies.

skill.name: Riposte
skill.desc: Fiora becomes immune to damage and spells. After a short delay, she stuns and damages the closest enemy

skill.name: Powder Kegs
skill.desc: Gangplank periodically creates barrels. On cast, Gangplank detonates the barrels, damaging nearby enemies. Applies on hit effects.

skill.name: Judgement
skill.desc: Garen spins his sword around for 4s, becoming immune to magic damage and dealing damage to nearby enemies.

skill.name: GNAR!
skill.desc: Gnar transforms, gaining Health, Attack Damage and jumping behind the furthest enemy, damaging and stunning enemies nearby for 2s.

skill.name: Buckshot
skill.desc: Innate: Graves' attacks deal increased damage and hit all enemies in front of him.

skill.name: Meercury Cannon
skill.desc: Jayce knocks away an emeny in melee range, dealing damage and stunning them for few seconds. He then transforms his hammer into a cannon, increasing his attack range by 3 hexes and gaining max attackspeed for few attacks.

skill.name: Get Excited!
skill.desc: Jinx gets excited as participates in kills: On her first takedown, she gains attack speed. On her second, she swaps to her rocket launcher causing her attacks to deal bonus area damage

skill.name: Killer Instinct
skill.desc: Kai'Sa dashes to the farthest enemy unit, gaining a damage shield and Attack Speed for 3 seconds.

skill.name: Requiem
skill.desc: Karthus deals damage to a number of random enemies after a long channel.

skill.name: Nether Blade
skill.desc: Kassadin's attacks steal mana from enemies, converting it into a shield that lasts for 4s.

skill.name: Death Lotus
skill.desc: Katarina channels for 2.5s and fires daggers at a number of nearby enemies, dealing damage and reducing healing.

skill.name: Divine Judgement
skill.desc: Kayle shields the weakest ally, making them immune to damage.

skill.name: Slicing Maelstrom
skill.desc: Kennen summons a storm around him, dealing damage and stunning enemies inside of it for 1.5s.

skill.name: Taste their Fear
skill.desc: Kha'Zix slashes the closest enemy, dealing bonus damage to enemies that are alone

skill.name: Lamb's Respite
skill.desc: Kindred creates a zone around herself that prevents allies from dying.

skill.name: Solar Flare
skill.desc: Leona calls down a solar ray that damages and slows enemies inside it. The enemy in the center is stunned.

skill.name: Frozen Tomb
skill.desc: Lissandra encases the target in ice for 1.5s, dealing damage to nearby enemies. Below half HP, Lissandra instead encases herself, becoming untargetable for 2s.

skill.name: Relentless Pursuit
skill.desc: Lucian dashes away to safety and attacks an enemy twice, once with Attack Damage and once with Spell Damage.

skill.name: Wild Growth
skill.desc: Lulu grants an ally bonus Health, knocking up enemies near them for 1.25s.

skill.name: Bullet Time
skill.desc: Miss Fortune channels for 3s, firing several waves of bullets damaging enemies in a cone.

skill.name: Obliterate
skill.desc: Mordekaiser slams his mace in front him, dealing damage to two enemies in a line.

skill.name: Soul Shackles
skill.desc: Morgana fires chains to nearby enemies, dealing damage and stunning after a short delay if they are still nearby.

skill.name: Primal Surge
skill.desc: Nidalee heals herself and the weakest ally, then transforms gaining Attack Damage.

skill.name: Grand Starfall
skill.desc: Pantheon leaps in the air, crashing down towards the farthest enemy, stunning them. Enemies in Pantheon's path take % of their Maximum Health as Magic Damage. They then burn for an additional 20% of their Maximum Health as True Damage over 10 seconds. Applies Grievous Wounds.

skill.name: Keeper's Verdict
skill.desc: Poppy swings her hammer, damaging and knocking up the closest enemy.

skill.name: Phantom Undertow
skill.desc: Pyke dashes behind the furthest enemy, creating an afterimage that stuns enemies it passes through.

skill.name: Burrow
skill.desc: Rek'Sai burrows for a short duration becoming untargetable and healing. When Rek'Sai unburrows she deals damage and knocks up the closest enemy for 1.75s.

skill.name: Savagery
skill.desc: Rengar leaps to the lowest health enemy and stabs them for bonus on-hit damage. After dealing damage, Rengar gains Attack Speed and 25% Critical Strike Chance.

skill.name: Glacial Prison
skill.desc: Sejuani creates a large glacial storm, stunning enemies within it after a short delay.

skill.name: Spirit's Refuge
skill.desc: Shen creates a zone around himself, allowing allies to dodge all attacks

skill.name: Dragon's Descent
skill.desc: Shyvana dashes and transforms, gaining Attack Damage and Attack Range. When transformed, her attacks set enemies on fire.

skill.name: Demonflare
skill.desc: Swain transforms, draining health from all nearby enemies. At the end of his transformation, Swain sends out a burst of energy dealing damage to nearby enemies.

skill.name: Explosive Charge
skill.desc: Tristana places a bomb on her current target that detonates after 3 attacks, damaging nearby enemies.

skill.name: Pick a Card
skill.desc: Twisted Fate throws a card that either stuns, deals damage around his target, or restores mana to himself and nearby allies

skill.name: Piercing Arrow
skill.desc: Varus charges and fires an arrow, dealing damage to all enemies in a line.

skill.name: Silver Bolts
skill.desc: Innate: Vayne deals bonus true damage every third attack based on the enemy's maximum health.

skill.name: Primordial Burst
skill.desc: Veigar blasts an enemy with magical energy, dealing damage. This spell instantly kills if the enemy is a lower star level than Veigar.

skill.name: Assault and Battery
skill.desc: Vi charges down the furthest enemy, knocking aside anyone in her way. When she reaches her target, she deals magic damage and knocks them up. Other enemies knocked aside take the same damage.

skill.name: Thunder Claws
skill.desc: Volibear empowers his attacks to chain between enemies, applying on-hit effects.

skill.name: Infinite Duress
skill.desc: Warwick pounces onto the lowest health enemy, stunning them for 1.5s, damaging them and healing himself. Applies on-hit effects.

skill.name: Tempest Steel
skill.desc: Yasuo stabs forward, damaging two enemies in a line. On third cast, Yasuo instead launches a tornado dealing damage and knocking up enemies in a line for 1.5s. Applies on hit effects.

skill.name: Razor Shuriken
skill.desc: Zed throws a shuriken, dealing damage to enemies in a line.
